Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:39.74,EDTitle,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,220)\pos(315,240)}在战斗之中
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------SUB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界真正的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这单片眼镜借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称为「坂井悠二」的人类究竟是不是火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请自己去确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要现在你来协助我们看来是没可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像小姐这样在这个城市土生土长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保留着这个城市纯粹的印象的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才适合进行调律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学是火炬的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学没事的…一定没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在明天的祭典上一定要对坂井同学说「我喜欢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把目标放在悠二身上的「化装舞会」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混进这城市里的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里原本已经不平衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得更糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不能再待在这城市里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有「化装舞会」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也已经不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天必须和母亲以及大家分别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想暂时在这里…和平时一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天穿上和服让悠二大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一起去祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了离开这里的时候也…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起离开这城市？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈  这还真是迷得彻底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们  应该明白这意味着什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的目标就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能使用这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就带我们走是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不是绕着圈子叫我们别跟去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换作平时的你不就一顿臭揍了结的嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样看来明天会下酒雨咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  祭典穿不穿和服去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为买新的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说要离开这城市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天5点在桥那里碰头怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那小姑娘如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫坂井悠二的男人不是火炬便好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  能冷静到可以帮忙的程度就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调律这城市稍微有点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  歪曲得异常严重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在这附近也打上印记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再打一两个应该够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过  不光是歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有某些不协和感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止可谓是一帆风顺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离准备完成还剩6小时14分32秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这花纹非常合适
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见这么漂亮的小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠真得会吓一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小悠好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经有离开城市的心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却很痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已经那么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期六一直是下午开始锻炼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会早回来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他说过今天晚上开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去祭典的事没告诉过他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是闲逛去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲逛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去找小悠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和池他们在缘日玩也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}缘日：参拜神佛的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下便条的话就算错过也不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里遇见的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠会更吃惊也说不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜  看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠缘日来的话绝对会买的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃吃看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要妨碍我们训练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是来祭典玩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人说要出门的话就乖乖跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且啊  再那样继续的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会做出一道难看的活「人」刺身咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荣太  去买点酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝酒么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方  走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有苹果糖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想知道…坂井同学到底有没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…这样下去就…永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  剩下的就是等待那位小姐的协助了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  仍然很介意这不协和感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是歪曲太厉害的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有红世之徒的气息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前为止还没有办法对付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类还真好用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连一个火雾战士都没察觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授  准备完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就对坂井同学好好说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我喜欢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来都没任何气息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草  我想起还有件事要办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是红世之徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但放出了自在式却没有气息是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概藏在什么地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  放松心情就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  我们去玻璃坛就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要查出红世之徒的位置就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全给看穿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用法已经知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  不是真打算带他们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是临时应急用用罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平时一样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说也需要用玻璃坛来调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这自在式还真大手笔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设下这么大的机关  看来不是普通人物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二也一定察觉到了  到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是红世之徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先要通知夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田…同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人…坂井同学…骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田一美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么吉田一美会和悠二在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吉田同学知道了我是火炬的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快去追她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事…别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧  红世之徒开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须对吉田同学解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二一定要和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要对吉田一美那种人解释
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们无关的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无关？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和吉田一美毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都没所谓啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到夏娜会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说并不是无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「仪装之驱手」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好久不见了呢  「天壤劫火」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也被这自在式…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔克希亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总对这乱七八糟的自在式有不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…「探耽求究」——丹塔里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是那个神经病教授没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那家伙的气息完全感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来更加需要玻璃坛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧一点吧  启作  荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中那家伙跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绪什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不说给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才和你在一起的女人的事就不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了只是认识而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:17:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在蒙混了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…小绪  我可要生气咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我介意啊…非常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说到底为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为喜欢田中荣太！所以才介意呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学是…火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学  到底谁把这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红世之徒的攻击可已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  继续刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这自在式使得歪曲更厉害了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市将会被严重到不能修复的歪曲给吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底为了什么而这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有对策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  只要开始调律就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必要的印记已经打完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需一位能将城市正常姿态印象化的协助者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  实际上已经有心目中的人选了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微出了点纰漏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫作吉田一美的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  她身上带着的气息原来是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她来的话调律马上就能开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为火雾战士的使命会好好完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该是火雾战士们来捣乱的时候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白了没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  开始着手第二作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法马上给你答复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  待会会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在封绝中还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  必须做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能办到么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…缘？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤  来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  热闹起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后会变成什么样还真令人期待啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.89,0:24:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在仍旧无法捕捉到教授的行踪之际
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「混沌的圣庙」正在御崎市上空逐渐完成
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.19,0:24:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜作为火雾战士而战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.59,0:24:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉着逐渐远去悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  在战斗之中
